OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FForced adoptions: Call for 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgovernment apology to      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fmothers                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Hundreds of thousands of unmarried     
OL,6, women who were forced to give up their 
OL,7, babies for adoption should receive a   
OL,8, government apology, a report has said. 
OL,10,FThe inquiry, by the Joint Committee on 
OL,11,FHuman Rights, was set up following a   
OL,12,Fseries of reports by BBC News.         
OL,14,FIt says 185,000 women in the 1950s, 60s
OL,15,Fand 70s were "shamed" and "coerced"    
OL,16,Finto giving up their babies.           
OL,18,FMany say they were denied pain relief  
OL,19,Fduring birth and abused by social      
OL,20,Fworkers, nurses and other staff.       
